'''Abd al-Malik al-Muzaffar''' was [[hajib]] of the [[Caliphate of Cordoba]] from the death of his father [[al-Mansur ibn Abi Aamir]] (known to later Spanish historians as Almanzor) in 1002 until his own death in 1008. He was succeeded by his half-brother [[Abd al-Rahman Sanchuelo]].

